{"tid":1128320,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"突發! 復仇者聯盟5故事大綱曝光!! 絕對係你異想不到!","createTime":"2019-04-27T17:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T22:37:12.000Z","uid":132174,"like":41,"dislike":600,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"93115a47106cde4b1dc66e79139ffcb7f4129415","tid":1128320,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:43:42.000Z","msg":"事先聲明我個朋友係Marvel員工，冒着生命危險爆俾我聽，唔信可以唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n終局之戰五年後，世界大致回復和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。令一邊廂，Ironman，黑寡婦同Thanos 喺地府玩緊鬥地主，過住優哉游哉嘅生活。突然，遠處傳來一陣騷亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來是 Michael Jackson 帶着佢嘅thriller 喪屍大軍，連同落咗地府嘅689同柒婆想要統治地下世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />閻羅王同一眾牛頭馬面已經失守！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在絕望中主角三人決定挺身而出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但由於地府缺乏武器，Ironman 情急之下只好報夢比pepper 叫佢燒件紙紮裝甲落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Thanos 則馬上趕造紙紮手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幸好的是黑寡婦本來就係佈景板所以影響不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟他們能否成功再一次阻止災難降臨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be55002c77ff2e5a7f968421ce2119b8dea32f67","tid":1128320,"uid":132174,"like":4,"dislike":40,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:44:44.000Z","msg":"睇到個故事大綱已經想射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2204e7721fea376a698c5a5e0103f9aaf9ad6b","tid":1128320,"uid":30274,"like":192,"dislike":3,"score":1